## AssembledFeatureOf type

A lookup type to infer the assembled feature from a feature.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type AssembledFeatureOf<F> = F extends Feature<infer O, infer S, infer P> ? AssembledFeature<O, S, P> : never;
```
